  <brief_title>The Effects of Azithromycin Ophthalmic Solution, 1% Versus Placebo in Subjects With Blepharitis During a Four-Week Treatment Period (P08638)</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to compare the safety and efficacy of azithromycin ophthalmic
      solution, 1% versus placebo over a four-week treatment period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
